         <div type="traslation">
            <head>Translation</head>
            <p>[Number of] grandhas 1500. Honour to the illustrious Raṃganāthaparabrahman
               together with Raṃganāyakī. The <foreign xml:lang="san-Latn"
                  >Yādavagirimāhātmyam</foreign> is complete. Honour to the illustrious
               Veṃkaṭāryyamahādeśika. It was fully copied in the year called Śārvarī, month of
               Mākha, 19th day. Śrīnivāsan copied with his own hand.</p>
         </div>
